ABOUT
=====

Gecko has built-in cross platform profiling support.
This extension is designed to prevent a front end
to this profiling support.

For more details see:
https://developer.mozilla.org/en/Performance/Profiling_with_the_Built-in_Profiler

PLATFORM
========

For the platform support see 'tools/profiler' in gecko.

INSTALLING
==========

In order to install this add-on, you need a copy of the add-on SDK.  Please do the following:

1. `git clone https://github.com/mozilla/addon-sdk`
2. `git checkout 1.4`
    Add the following to 'sdk/packages':
      - https://github.com/erikvold/xulkeys-jplib
      - https://github.com/erikvold/vold-utils-jplib
3. `. bin/activate`
4. `cd /path/to/Gecko-Profiler-Addon`
5. `cfx xpi`
